EXERIENCE  based testing:
THE have the past exper and common general  knowledge and the  projject with the help of this they can improve the quality of data.

Experience based testing techniques:
1.Error guesting:  identify the error on they past experience of the tester and developer and shak holders  on the general  common programing knowledge.
2. EXplorting testing: they learn about it and design on the past experience with common programming knowledge.
3.checklist based testing : they are pre defind the check list how to run and executed on the past project experience.
4.Attack  testing : it is a negative testing  they given invalid  input to broken the system  they try lot  of attemp.

when to use :
1. tight time line.
2. limited resources.
3.limited bud get.

 when not not use:
1.changing of the requirement.
2.regular complain.
3. new technologies.
